# Check AGENTS.md Before Implementation

Before implementing any change or writing code:

1. **Read [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md)** at the project root for:
   - Working process (branch policy, no AI attribution in commits/PRs)
   - Relevant docs (ARCHITECTURE, CONVENTIONS, SECURITY, etc.)
   - Key invariants (Zod-first types, COLLECTIONS, soft delete, indexes)

2. **Apply it**: Create a new branch when starting a task; follow conventions and invariants; never add AI/editor attribution to commits or PRs.

Do not skip this step. If you have not read AGENTS.md in this session, read it before making edits or running non-readonly commands.
